!        will be complete for temperature, WS, WD and Scalar WS.
!        Issue arises when multi-level on-site data is used in AERMET
!        and levels are not complete for all variables.  For instance
!        records are present for 2 meter temperature and 10 meter winds.
!        MODIFIED: RDMET4, RDMET5
