!
!
!     Direct solution for urban dispersion                              isc36880
170   go to (180,180,190,200,200,200), kst                             ! isc36890
!     Solution to the cubic equation                                    isc36900
!     from CRC mathematical tables                                      isc36910
!     stability a&b (180)                                               isc36920
