      subroutine restarto
!----------------------------------------------------------------------
!
! --- CALPUFF    Version: 7.3.1        Level: 080520          RESTARTO
! ---            D. Strimaitis
!
! --- PURPOSE:  Output all data needed to restart CALPUFF with
