      subroutine restarti
!----------------------------------------------------------------------
!
! --- CALPUFF    Version: 7.3.1        Level: 080520          RESTARTI
! ---            D. Strimaitis
!
! --- PURPOSE:  Input all data needed to restart CALPUFF with
!               current puffs in the domain
!
! --- UPDATE
! --- V6.22-V6.261  080520  (DGS): Replace source-ordered tabulations
