!----------------------------------------------------------------------
!
! --- CALPUFF    Version: 7.3.1        Level: 140521              AUX1
!                D. Strimaitis
!
! --- PURPOSE:  Read header records of auxiliary CALMET meteorological
!               data file
!
! --- UPDATES:
